            <p>
              Most cameras are compatible, so combine your webcams and IP cameras and make the most of your system.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
            <h3 class="content-subhead">
              <i class="fa fa-inbox"></i>
              Stay in the loop
            </h3>
            <p>
              Receive alerts when your cameras detect movement via email or SMS, with webhook support coming soon.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
            <h3 class="content-subhead">
              <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
              View from anywhere
