              View live feeds of your cameras from anywhere in the world with internet access on any smartphone or computer.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
            <h3 class="content-subhead">
              <i class="fa fa-calendar-o"></i>
